channel.title: [Help!] Adding Models (Good explanation with pictures)
channel.description:
Ok Guys I really need your help getting my master sword in runescape I have been working on this for days now :D. I have just gotten the drop model to show up and not dc me from my client. Now when I do get it working my wield model effs up on me :/ It turns me invisible. There is no error on the clients cmd prompt or anything Im just invisible [img]http://i347.photobucket.com/albums/p460/frogtamer101/setup.jpg[/img] Theres all I can show really just a collage of the things I need to show. I set the priorities to 10 and the animation to right hand and for the drop model it is set to no animation and 0 for the pri :/
HELP!
